data.eml:eml: Three new species of Aponuphis (Annelida: Onuphidae) from eastern Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal volume Paxton, Hannelore (2017): Three new species of Aponuphis (Annelida: Onuphidae) from eastern Australia. Zootaxa 4344 (2), DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4344.2.2
